<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Backerss — Dashboard Academia</title>
  <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="favicon.png">
  
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg-main: #0B0B0A;
      --bg-card: #141412;
      --accent: #E5C158;
      --accent-bright: #F0CC5B;
      --text-primary: #F5F5F3;
      --text-muted: #8A8A85;
      --border: #262622;
      --success: #3EE587;
      --bg-raised: #1A1A16;
    }

    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    body {
      background-color: var(--bg-main);
      color: var(--text-primary);
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.35;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    .mono {
      font-family: "SFMono-Regular", Consolas, "Liberation Mono", Menlo, monospace;
    }

    header {
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 0 auto 25px auto;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding-bottom: 20px;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      letter-spacing: -0.5px;
    }

    .vault-chip {
      background: #1A1A16;
      border: 1px solid var(--accent);
      padding: 8px 16px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: flex-end;
    }

    .vault-label {
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .vault-amount {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      color: var(--accent);
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    .dashboard-layout {
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 25px;
    }

    /* ---------- SECCIÓN ARSENAL DE INICIO (VALUE STACK) ---------- */
    .arsenal-card {
      background: var(--bg-card);
      border: 1px solid rgba(229, 193, 88, 0.2);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 20px;
      position: relative;
    }

    .arsenal-title {
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      color: var(--accent);
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      font-weight: bold;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 6px;
    }

    .arsenal-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .arsenal-item {
      background: #0F0F0E;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 12px 14px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      transition: all 0.2s ease;
    }

    .arsenal-item:hover {
      border-color: var(--accent);
      background: #161614;
    }

    .ai-info {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 2px;
    }

    .ai-name {
      font-size: 0.88rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--text-primary);
    }

    .ai-tag {
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      color: var(--text-muted);
    }

    .btn-download {
      background: transparent;
      border: none;
      color: var(--accent);
      cursor: pointer;
      padding: 4px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      transition: color 0.2s;
    }
    .btn-download:hover { color: var(--text-primary); }

    /* ---------- CONSTELACIÓN COLECTIVA ---------- */
    .constellation-card {
      background: var(--bg-card);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 24px;
    }

    .constellation-head {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .constellation-field {
      background: #0F0F0E;
      border: 1px dashed var(--border);
      border-radius: 8px;
      min-height: 120px;
      padding: 16px;
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 10px;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .backer-node {
      background: #1A2E22;
      border: 1px solid var(--success);
      padding: 6px 12px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 6px;
      animation: fadeIn 0.3s ease-out;
    }

    .backer-node .dot {
      width: 8px;
      height: 8px;
      background: var(--success);
      border-radius: 50%;
      box-shadow: 0 0 8px var(--success);
    }

    .backer-node .tag {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: var(--text-primary);
    }

    .add-backer-btn {
      background: #1A1A16;
      border: 1px dashed var(--accent);
      color: var(--accent);
      padding: 6px 16px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      cursor: pointer;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      transition: background 0.2s;
    }

    .add-backer-btn:hover {
      background: #262620;
    }

    /* ---------- TARJETAS DE MISIONES ---------- */
    .mission-card {
      background: var(--bg-card);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 24px;
      position: relative;
      transition: opacity 0.3s;
    }

    .mission-card.is-locked {
      opacity: 0.35;
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .mission-card.is-locked::after {
      content: "🔒 Bloqueado — Completa la misión anterior";
      position: absolute;
      top: 15px;
      right: 20px;
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      background: #1A1A16;
      padding: 4px 10px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
    }

    .mission-head {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .mission-tag {
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      color: var(--accent);
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    .mission-days {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: var(--text-muted);
    }

    .mission-title {
      font-size: 1.35rem;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      letter-spacing: -0.3px;
    }

    .mission-desc {
      color: var(--text-muted);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    .mission-video-link {
      background: #1C1C18;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      width: 100%;
      padding: 12px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
      cursor: pointer;
      color: var(--text-primary);
      text-align: left;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    .mvl-icon {
      background: var(--accent);
      width: 32px;
      height: 32px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .mvl-text {
      font-weight: bold;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }

    .mvl-sub {
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      color: var(--text-muted);
    }

    /* ---------- ENLACE DE CAPTURA ---------- */
    .capture-card {
      background: #0F0F0E;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 16px;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    .capture-card-head {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .cc-badge {
      color: var(--success);
    }

    .capture-link-row {
      display: flex;
      gap: 10px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .capture-link-box {
      background: #141412;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding: 10px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      flex-grow: 1;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: var(--accent);
      overflow-x: auto;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .copy-link-btn {
      background: var(--text-primary);
      color: var(--bg-main);
      border: none;
      padding: 0 16px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-weight: bold;
      cursor: pointer;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 6px;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }

    .cc-hint {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: var(--text-muted);
    }

    .goal-strip {
      display: flex;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 8px;
      overflow: hidden;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .goal-cell {
      flex: 1;
      padding: 12px;
      background: #0F0F0E;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .goal-cell:first-child {
      border-right: 1px solid var(--border);
    }

    .goal-num {
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: var(--text-primary);
    }

    .goal-label {
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      margin-top: 2px;
    }

    /* ---------- CHECKLISTS SYSTEM ---------- */
    .checklist {
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding-top: 18px;
    }

    .checklist-head {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    .check-item {
      display: flex;
      gap: 12px;
      padding: 12px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      cursor: pointer;
      background: #0F0F0E;
      transition: background 0.2s, border-color 0.2s;
    }

    .check-item:hover {
      background: #141412;
      border-color: #33332D;
    }

    .check-box {
      width: 20px;
      height: 20px;
      border: 2px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 4px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      flex-shrink: 0;
      margin-top: 2px;
    }

    .check-box svg {
      width: 14px;
      height: 14px;
      display: none;
      color: var(--bg-main);
    }

    .check-item.checked .check-box {
      background: var(--accent);
      border-color: var(--accent);
    }

    .check-item.checked .check-box svg {
      display: block;
    }

    .check-label {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }

    .check-meta {
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    }

    /* ---------- DIAGNÓSTICO ABIERTO ---------- */
    .diagnostic-options {
      display: flex;
      gap: 8px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }

    .diag-btn {
      background: #1C1C18;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      color: var(--text-muted);
      padding: 6px 14px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      cursor: pointer;
      font-family: monospace;
      transition: all 0.2s;
    }

    .diag-btn:hover {
      border-color: #444;
      color: var(--text-primary);
    }

    .diag-btn.active {
      background: #2E2714;
      border-color: var(--accent);
      color: var(--accent);
      font-weight: bold;
      box-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(229, 193, 88, 0.15);
    }

    .action-row {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: flex-end;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }

    .complete-btn {
      background: #1F1F1A;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding: 14px 28px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-weight: bold;
      cursor: not-allowed;
      transition: all 0.3s;
    }

    .complete-btn.is-ready {
      background: var(--accent);
      color: var(--bg-main);
      cursor: pointer;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 14px rgba(229, 193, 88, 0.2);
    }

    /* ---------- TOAST ALERTS ---------- */
    .toast {
      position: fixed;
      bottom: -60px;
      left: 50%;
      transform: translateX(-50%);
      background: var(--success);
      color: var(--bg-main);
      padding: 12px 24px;
      border-radius: 30px;
      font-weight: bold;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(62, 229, 135, 0.3);
      transition: bottom 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.175, 0.885, 0.32, 1.275);
      z-index: 100;
    }

    .toast.is-visible {
      bottom: 30px;
    }

    @keyframes fadeIn {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: scale(0.9); }
      to { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <header>
    <div>
      <h1 class="mono">BACKERSS ACADEMY</h1>
      <p style="font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--text-muted);">Entrenamiento de Alto Rendimiento</p>
    </div>
    <div class="vault-chip">
      <span class="vault-label mono">Mi Bóveda</span>
      <span class="vault-amount mono" id="vaultAmount">$0</span>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main class="dashboard-layout">

    <section class="arsenal-card">
      <div class="arsenal-title">
        <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M22 19a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H4a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h5l2 3h9a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"/></svg>
        Tu Arsenal de Inicio — Material Incluido
      </div>
      <div class="arsenal-grid">
        <div class="arsenal-item">
          <div class="ai-info">
            <span class="ai-name">Manual: Organiza Tu Vida</span>
            <span class="ai-tag mono">PDF EBOOK DETALLADO</span>
          </div>
          <button class="btn-download" title="Descargar material">
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M21 15v4a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v4M7 10l5 5 5-5M12 15V3"/></svg>
          </button>
        </div>
        <div class="arsenal-item">
          <div class="ai-info">
            <span class="ai-name">Mapa de Transformación</span>
            <span class="ai-tag mono">INFOGRAFÍA PUNTO A -> B</span>
          </div>
          <button class="btn-download" title="Descargar material">
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M21 15v4a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v4M7 10l5 5 5-5M12 15V3"/></svg>
          </button>
        </div>
        <div class="arsenal-item">
          <div class="ai-info">
            <span class="ai-name">Checklist de Pared</span>
            <span class="ai-tag mono">IMPRIMIBLE DE ACCIÓN DIARIA</span>
          </div>
          <button class="btn-download" title="Descargar material">
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M21 15v4a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v4M7 10l5 5 5-5M12 15V3"/></svg>
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <div class="constellation-card">
      <div class="constellation-head">
        <h3 class="mono">Tu Constelación Colectiva</h3>
        <span class="mono" id="constellationCount" style="color: var(--accent); font-size: 0.9rem;">0 Backers</span>
      </div>
      <div class="constellation-field" id="constellationField">
        <button type="button" class="add-backer-btn mono" id="addBackerBtn">+ Simular Registro Externo ($12)</button>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="dashboard-layout" style="gap: 20px;">

      <div class="mission-card" id="cardReto1">
        <div class="mission-head">
          <div class="mission-tag">Misión activa · Reto 1</div>
          <div class="mission-days mono">Días 1–3 · Meta mínima</div>
        </div>
        <div class="mission-body">
          <h2 class="mission-title">El Baño de Realidad</h2>
          <p class="mission-desc">Tu única meta: conseguir al menos 20 contactos reales desde tu página de captura. No estás cazando un “no” ni un “sí” — estás cazando el contacto número 20 como tu primera victoria. Cada contacto adicional es práctica y confianza extra en tu ecosistema.</p>

          <button type="button" class="mission-video-link">
            <span class="mvl-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="16" height="16" fill="#0B0B0A"><path d="M8 5v14l11-7z"/></svg></span>
            <span>
              <span class="mvl-text">Ver Video Briefing — Misión 1</span><br>
              <span class="mvl-sub">60 SEG · CONTEXTO, OBJETIVO Y POR QUÉ</span>
            </span>
          </button>

          <div class="capture-card">
            <div class="capture-card-head">
              <span class="cc-title font-weight-bold">Tu página de captura</span>
              <span class="cc-badge mono">Lista para usar</span>
            </div>
            <div class="capture-link-row">
              <div class="capture-link-box mono" id="captureLinkText">backerss.com/captura.html?ref=<span style="color: #fff;">TU-NOMBRE</span></div>
              <button type="button" class="copy-link-btn" id="copyLinkBtn">Copiar</button>
            </div>
            <p class="cc-hint">Comparte este link con tu tráfico frío. Cuando alguien deje sus datos ahí, entra directo a tu Constelación.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="goal-strip">
            <div class="goal-cell">
              <div class="goal-num mono" id="contactCount">0 / 20</div>
              <div class="goal-label">Contactos reales · mínimo</div>
            </div>
            <div class="goal-cell">
              <div class="goal-num mono">Día 1</div>
              <div class="goal-label">De 3 (techo máximo)</div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="checklist">
            <div class="checklist-head">
              <span>Compromiso de ejecución</span>
              <span class="mono" id="checklistCount">0 / 4</span>
            </div>

            <div class="check-item normal-check">
              <div class="check-box"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><path d="M5 12l5 5L20 7"/></svg></div>
              <div class="check-text">
                <div class="check-label">Personalicé mi mini página con mi nombre, foto y verifiqué mi enlace único</div>
                <div class="check-meta mono">INFRAESTRUCTURA LISTA — CONFIGURACIÓN INICIAL</div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="check-item normal-check">
              <div class="check-box"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><path d="M5 12l5 5L20 7"/></svg></div>
              <div class="check-text">
                <div class="check-label">Publiqué mi enlace en al menos 2 canales activos usando el texto sugerido</div>
                <div class="check-meta mono">ROMPER LA INERCIA — LANZAMIENTO INICIAL ACTIVADO</div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="check-item normal-check">
              <div class="check-box"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><path d="M5 12l5 5L20 7"/></svg></div>
              <div class="check-text">
                <div class="check-label">Comprendo el marco teórico: mi éxito es acumular volumen de datos, no buscar aprobación</div>
                <div class="check-meta mono">BLINDAJE MENTAL — ADQUISICIÓN DE PERSPECTIVA COMERCIAL</div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="check-item custom-diagnostic" id="diagnosticItem">
              <div class="check-box" id="diagnosticCheckBox"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><path d="M5 12l5 5L20 7"/></svg></div>
              <div class="check-text" style="width: 100%;">
                <div class="check-label">Registré el resultado de mi primera interacción o conversación con el mercado</div>
                <div class="check-meta mono" style="margin-bottom: 10px;">APRENDIZAJE REAL — SELECCIONA EL ESCENARIO REAL QUE VIVISTE:</div>
                
                <div class="diagnostic-options" onclick="event.stopPropagation();">
                  <button type="button" class="diag-btn" data-type="incov">A) Incómoda / Objeciones</button>
                  <button type="button" class="diag-btn" data-type="exito">B) Exitosa / Fluida</button>
                  <button type="button" class="diag-btn" data-type="no-obj">C) Sin Objeciones</button>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="action-row">
            <button type="button" class="complete-btn mono" id="completeBtn">Completar Reto 1</button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mission-card is-locked" id="cardReto2">
        <div class="mission-head">
          <div class="mission-tag">Reto 2</div>
          <div class="mission-days mono">Días 4–10 · Comisiones</div>
        </div>
        <div class="mission-body">
          <h2 class="mission-title">Tu primera comisión en 48 horas</h2>
          <p class="mission-desc">Filtra tus 20 capturas iniciales y ejecuta el script de inversión cooperativa para activar tu sistema económico mutuo.</p>
          
          <div class="checklist">
            <div class="checklist-head">
              <span>Compromiso de ejecución · Reto 2</span>
              <span class="mono">0 / 4</span>
            </div>
            <div class="check-item">
              <div class="check-box"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><path d="M5 12l5 5L20 7"/></svg></div>
              <div class="check-text"><div class="check-label">Identifiqué y contacté a los 5 perfiles con mayor potencial de mi lista de 20 capturas iniciales</div><div class="check-meta mono">FILTRADO DE DATOS</div></div>
            </div>
            <div class="check-item">
              <div class="check-box"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><path d="M5 12l5 5L20 7"/></svg></div>
              <div class="check-text"><div class="check-label">Envié la propuesta de valor usando el script de "inversión cooperativa"</div><div class="check-meta mono">MECÁNICA COMERCIAL</div></div>
            </div>
            <div class="check-item">
              <div class="check-box"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><path d="M5 12l5 5L20 7"/></svg></div>
              <div class="check-text"><div class="check-label">Gestioné mi primer rechazo directo entendiendo que es parte de la estadística</div><div class="check-meta mono">BLINDAJE EMOCIONAL</div></div>
            </div>
            <div class="check-item">
              <div class="check-box"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><path d="M5 12l5 5L20 7"/></svg></div>
